  <!-- Latest jobs -->
  <div class="row">

    <div class="contented">

      <div class="rhythmic-xxl">

        <h1 class="h1  mobile-h1--s  font--bold  rhythmic-s  mobile-rhythmic-xxs  rhythm-m-1  text-center  inview-fade">Latest jobs</h1>

        <div class="rhythm-m-2  mobile-rhythm-m-1-half">

          
            <div class="gutted-xxl  mobile-gutted  rhythmic  mobile-rhythmic-s  bordered  bg-white  rhythm-m-1  card  inview-fade">

              <h2 class="h3  font--bold  rhythm-m-0-half  rhythmic-xxs  mobile-tight  card__title">Head of Retail (Home)</h2>


              <div class="divider-b  rhythmic-xxs">

                <div class="grid">

                  <div class="grid__item  width-1/6  tablet-width-1/4  mobile-block">

                    <p class="p  font--bold">Location</p>

                  </div><!--

                  --><div class="grid__item  width-5/6  tablet-width-3/4  mobile-block">

                    <p class="p  font--bold  text-brand-primary">
                      Reigate                    </p>

                  </div>

                </div>

              </div>

              <div class="divider-b  rhythmic-xxs  rhythm-m-1">

                <div class="grid">

                  <div class="grid__item  width-1/6  tablet-width-1/4  mobile-block">

                    <p class="p  font--bold">Type</p>

                  </div><!--

                  --><div class="grid__item  width-5/6  tablet-width-3/4  mobile-block">

                    <p class="p  font--bold  text-brand-primary">Full-time</p>

                  </div>

                </div>

              </div>

              <div class="ps  font--bold  rhythm-m-0-half  tablet-rhythm-m-1  text-limit  mobile-hidden">
                                <p>Reporting to the Retail Director as part of the Retail Leadership team with accountability for the strategic design, development and implementation of the specific product line, ensuring close alignment with the wider business (in particular, U/W, Pricing, Operations, Finance & Claims) to increase and maximise their specific product revenue, promoting their product ( s)  throughout the customer lifecycle. Through aggregator, web and phone channels, achieve revenue and contribution targets and support all Retail plans to maximise the wider growth and total contribution to esure Group profit.</p>

<p><strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;">Responsibilities</span></strong></p>

<ul><li>Working with the Retail Director in the achievement of Retail Revenue and P&L targets as set by the Board. </li>
	<li>Responsible for producing plans and reporting, highlighting progress against target and future projections, both of which are communicated to the Op Exec, Group Exec and Board as appropriate.</li>
	<li>Drive for results focus, ensuring both projects and target numbers are met to deliver immediate and future targets.</li>
	<li>Production, development & maintenance of cross functional plans and reporting for their specific area, focused on both the in year and future year views.</li>
	<li>Provide analysis to support decision making and where needed producing MI to support logic.</li>
	<li>Lead cross-functional meetings, with a high level of stakeholder engagement to drive their areas and Retails delivery performance.</li>
	<li>Conduct regular competitor reviews.</li>
	<li>Design and develop Product strategy to achieve revenue targets supported by implementation plans, making changes as required through agreed governance and compliance processes , justified and commercial rationale, such as external benchmarking and internal performance analysis, and ensuring appropriate communications are in place and key stakeholders engaged. </li>
	<li>Accountable to the Retail Director for the management and performance of the specific product line against agreed targets through the production of reports and analysis showing results against targets and plans, attendance and contribution at steering group meetings and deputising for the Retail Director as required. </li>
	<li>Work across the Retail Team and other business areas to ensure full potential of product lines through appropriate channels and alignment to overall esure strategic plans, operational capability, external brand and sales delivery. </li>
	<li>Accountable for the development of new Product and propositions though undertaking market and competitor research, assessing the competitiveness and potential contribution to revenue </li>
	<li>Accountable for the successful implementation, delivery and future management of new products through cross  departmental and functional working and continued performance management of these products  against revenue targets.</li>
	<li>Responsible for the planning and creation of reporting requirements and the ongoing reporting and analysis of the agreed products by working with other esure functions to enable data interrogation, analysis, segmentations and an agreed Change control is in place. </li>
	<li>Accountable for working with the Operational Team to agree an inbound and outbound product revenue plan that has a focus on increased and growing contribution.</li>
	<li>Continually optimise on line conversation rate through influencing  marketing input, thorough and proven journey test against agreed outputs, regular competitor reviews and reacting to changes as a result of this activity, assessing the impact from new products on current products, ensuring appropriate Operations communications are produced. </li>
</ul><p> </p>              </div>

