<p>• Accountable for the Procurement and Supplier Management expertise in manage multiple Contracts, Projects and Categories for the business with values between £1m-£15m.<br />
• Responsible for sourcing decisions of a critical nature for the business, with annual Spend with external suppliers is c£230m.<br />
• Providing Procurement and Supplier Management representation to all departments and stakeholders across all esure locations.</p>              </div>

